<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Zyy Maple Leaf OS - 版本更新日志</title>
    <link href="//fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #D97706;
            --primary-hover: #B45309;
            --bg-card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --bg-card-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            --text-main: #F3F4F6;
            --text-muted: #9CA3AF;
            --border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%); /* 深色背景 */
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .back-btn {
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }
        .back-btn:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--primary-color); }

        main {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            flex: 1;
        }

        h1.page-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #ccc);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 2rem;
        }

        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: var(--border-color);
        }

        .version-block {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .version-block::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -2.35rem;
            top: 0.5rem;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.2);
        }

        .version-id {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .update-theme {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
        }

        .change-list {
            list-style: none;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .change-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .change-list li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        .change-list li::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .coming-soon .version-id {
            color: var(--secondary-color); /* 金色高亮 */
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1.page-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .version-id { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .timeline { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
            .version-block::before { left: -1.85rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <a href="//zyy.undz.cn/" class="logo">
            <img src="//zyy.undz.cn/images/pure_experience.png" alt="ZyyOS图标" height="40"> Zyy Maple Leaf OS
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">← 返回 Wiki 首页</a>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h1 class="page-title">版本更新日志</h1>

        <div class="timeline">

            <!-- 26N16 -->
            <div class="version-block coming-soon">
                <div class="version-id">26N16 <span style="font-size: 0.6em; opacity: 0.7; vertical-align: middle;">(即将到来)</span></div>
                <span class="update-theme">主题更新名称: 缤纷更新 (名称未定)</span>
                <ul class="change-list">
                    <li>在设置中添加了“随机壁纸”和“更多壁纸”</li>
                    <li>删除了“刷新桌面按钮”</li>
                    <li>修复了桌面应用显示bug</li>
                    <li>修复了应用库的显示bug</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 26N15 -->
            <div class="version-block">
                <div class="version-id">26N15</div>
                <span class="update-theme">主题更新名称: 计算器更新</span>
                <ul class="change-list">
                    <li>添加了计算器，并给计算器添加了根号</li>
                    <li>重构了计算器的“等于”计算逻辑</li>
                    <li>使这些窗口可移动：设置，计算器，系统更新日志</li>
                    <li>为“设置->感谢与成员->打开作者B站”添加了动画</li>
                    <li>删除了“设置进度”，并为设置页选项添加了选中造型</li>
                    <li>删除了程序文件读取器，我的世界游戏和共创世界</li>
                    <li>重构了桌面应用的逻辑</li>
                    <li>修改了浏览器的搜索引擎设置</li>
                    <li>调整小组件的大小</li>
                    <li>修改了OOBE界面</li>
                    <li>修复了5个已知Bug</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 26N14 -->
            <div class="version-block">
                <div class="version-id">26N14</div>
                <span class="update-theme">主题更新名称: 桌面更新</span>
                <ul class="change-list">
                    <li>修复了2个bug</li>
                    <li>添加了设置->应用->安装的应用</li>
                    <li>现在应用可以添加到桌面了</li>
                    <li>添加了共创世界</li>
                    <li>在登录页面添加了“重置账户”按钮</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 26N13 -->
            <div class="version-block">
                <div class="version-id">26N13</div>
                <span class="update-theme">主题更新名称: MC更新</span>
                <ul class="change-list">
                    <li>修复了1个bug</li>
                    <li>添加了我的世界游戏</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 26N09~26N12 -->
            <div class="version-block">
                <div class="version-id">26N09 ~ 26N12</div>
                <span class="update-theme">主题更新名称: 完善更新</span>
                <ul class="change-list">
                    <li>现在应用可以导入了</li>
                    <li>添加了文本编辑</li>
                    <li>给调节亮度和声音添加了动画</li>
                    <li>完善了大部分应用和功能</li>
                    <li>添加了程序文件读取器</li>
                    <li>添加了Zyy办公</li>
                    <li>给部分窗口UI适配了暗色模式</li>
                    <li>在设置中添加了ZyyAI设置</li>
                    <li>在设置中添加了应用选项</li>
                    <li>修复了12个已知bug</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
